                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">As per the poll on this site, and 3 others, the majority of players either do not care, or do NOT want this in the game.
<br />

<br />
Please, don't do this just because it's in other games.  Please listen to your playerbase, we see this in a way as "our" game, and we don't want this in OUR game.  Because it's in other games doesn't mean WE want it, and according to the polls, the majority don't want it or don't care.
<br />

<br />
Please, don't "fix" this, it is NOT broken!
<br />

<br />
On the other hand, the majority WOULD like to see the actual number of mana amount they themselves have.
<br />

<br />
Please, again, look at the poll in general, the majority here and on three other boards don't want this.
<br />

<br />
