From one of the posts you linked.  If it's an option you turn on and off, assuming the devs implement it right make it so when you turn it on your mana bar shows, when it's off your mana bar doesn't show, how is it a problem?  I'd love this for a raid or group situation, especially when I'm playing both myself and my cleric, would make it so that I no longer have even look at the cleric's screen to know if I'm good for more pulling or not.
<br />

<br />
